    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a new opcode in the Secure Shell terminal modes encoding.  The new opcode describes the widely used IUTF8 terminal mode bit, which indicates that terminal I/O uses UTF-8 character encoding.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
